&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Support the build-out of internal infrastructure and robust datasets that enable better, faster solutions for clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Contribute to the execution of live capital raise and M&amp;amp;A processes, working closely with senior bankers across deal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
